                  <summary>I) Taʾāmra Māryām “Miracles of Mary” (fols. 3ra-56rb)&#xD;
I-1) Maṣḥafa śǝrʿāt, Introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah (fols. 3ra-6va)&#xD;
I-2) Introductory exhortation (fols. 6va-9rb)&#xD;
I-3) ʾƎsaggǝd laki wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki... “I worship Thee…” (fols. 9va-10rb)&#xD;
I-4) Taʾāmra Māryām: 36 miracles (fols. 10rb-56rb)&#xD;
I-5) ʾAkkonu bǝʾǝsi... "Does not the man..." (distributed among the miracles of Mary, fols. 13vb-51va)</summary>
